{"tid":2413523,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"仆街capcom李小龍變支那國旗","createTime":"2021-02-18T18:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:10:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b7334f362bf58136979f0bb0ce71b451c85d4ea6","tid":2413523,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Capcom-Arcade-Stadium%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FCapcom-Arcade-Stadium%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%259C%25AC1.jpg&h=800c5f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&copy; CAPCOM CO., LTD. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.  剛於2021年2月18日推出，包含於《Capcom Arcade Stadium 》內的最新版本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCAPCOM 今日於Nintendo Switch推出《Capcom Arcade Stadium》！ 遊戲收錄共 32 款 CAPCOM 人氣大型電玩遊戲，官方強調今次的新作新增了多項原版遊戲所沒有、舒適而充實的功能及令人驚喜元素，玩家可以盡情回味兒時的懷舊情懷。不過有部分修改卻是令人吃驚，真正是「跟上時代」的修改。<br />\n<br />\n其實之前街霸亦已經「緊貼時代」，由之前英屬時期的香港旗，變成了特區區旗，想不到今次索性「超前進化」，直接跟春麗一同站於中國五星紅旗之下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「蘇聯佬」辛格夫的代表旗卻沒有變成俄羅斯。"},{"pid":"7ec13cee647cb3a39ac7ecc1bd110a12befacdd8","tid":2413523,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/switchsf2tred/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fswitchsf2tred%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=2fbafe71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/switchsf2tred/</a>"},{"pid":"ffba058ba1cd4d72b7f6d60be4826c58261fff22","tid":2413523,"uid":158411,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"再下一版直接寫China"},{"pid":"29a362211ecb9aeecfe205311fe6c81d6222ceb7","tid":2413523,"uid":97240,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jmso74.gif&am